ge and is required to be believed by the faithful the apparition at lourdes happened in four years later the most that might be claimed is that lourdes gave the infallible proclamation of a sort of heavenly stamp of approval but the church has never claimed that nor shall she in christ s peace brad kaiser bradk isdgsm eurpd csg mot com those who trust in him shall understand truth and the faithful shall abide with him in love because grace and mercy are with his holy ones and his care is with his elect wis nab
