globe she revealed herself in worldwide dispute with the forces of the dark she told catherine the times are evil misfortunes will fall upon france the throne will be overturned the entire world will be overcome by evils of all kinds refer to books on st catherine for more of our lady s messages a copy of the medal is also available in catholic bookstores i will post other marian events every few days or so including the ones happening today which are still under investigation these postings serve only to introduce you to these events please look more into them and understand the reason for the increasing number and urgency of these apparitions mark ashley disclaimer my opinions not harris marka gcx ssd csd harris com the lost los angelino
