as a mistake and that the permissive but not prescriptive legislation worked very well we are going to start going round the homosexual debate at next years assembly at this years a motion was put to ban the blessing of same sex couples after an edinburgh minister did so our panel on doctrine is currently looking at marriage and will report next year the matter will be considered and debated then hope this is interesting alison
