 legalizing a list of torture methods thus eliminating the fear that a detainee might be released if those methods were used to extract a confession the fact that the need to lie still persists would seem to indicate that shabak is not sticking to the approved torture methods yigal yigal arens usc isi tv made me do it arens isi edu
